<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bamboo Class by Rajinikanth</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .class-info {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .attractive-text {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3498db, #e74c3c);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="class-info">
        <h1>Welcome to the <span class="attractive-text">Bamboo Class</span></h1>
        <p>By <span class="highlight">Rajinikanth</span></p>
        <p>Trainer in <span class="highlight">DevOps, Cloud, ML-Ops, AI-Op</span></p>
        <p>In colorful mode, HD, attractively presented</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
